OL,5, Proposals to reform Whitehall have been
OL,6, met with eye rolling, disengagement and
OL,7, aversion tactics by top civil servants,
OL,8, a new report was told.                 
OL,10,FResistance to change from within is one
OL,11,Fof the key barriers to making the civil
OL,12,Fservice more efficient, the think tank 
OL,13,FReform reported.                       
OL,15,FBut a civil service union told the BBC 
OL,16,F"reform needs to be strategic" and "too
OL,17,Foften it is a knee-jerk reaction".     
OL,19,FA government spokesperson said its new 
OL,20,Freform programme is making progress.   
